{"tid":374417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港豬眼紅】美高梅：颶風襲澳期間工作的員工獲發3倍時薪人工","createTime":"2017-08-25T17:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T11:50:51.000Z","uid":29314,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64f5c53232f4ce65c873bedb4c38a61d38be0557","tid":374417,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:23:14.000Z","msg":"繼銀娛（027）及新濠（200）向員工發放津貼後，再有濠賭股發放津貼予員工。網上流傳美高梅（2282）亦向颶風襲澳期間工作的員工發放時薪三倍的人工。<br />\n<br />\nfb專頁《新澳門博彩員工權益會》流傳一張由美高梅向內部員工發出的指引，稱為表揚颶風襲澳期間員工的非凡工作表現，會發放一次性特別津貼及「ot補水」。若員工於周三及周四（8月23至24日）兩天，工作了半更以上，將發放相等於時薪3倍的人工；而不足半更者亦獲發相等於時薪兩倍的人工。另期間「ot補水」亦會由1.5倍時薪上調至3倍計算。"},{"pid":"0707401571f866e9936b50fff5bebbeb507cdf5a","tid":374417,"uid":22694,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:35:37.000Z","msg":"如果香港打風前出呢個offer<br />\n大把人爭住開工<br />\n同平日一樣"},{"pid":"eb4c1744e7c7fa462b842ba537a9a116b4988191","tid":374417,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:37:38.000Z","msg":"有無炒散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a9c755b2ccc1432c3868c2536eddd53469171e","tid":374417,"uid":14816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之啲人走去賭場返工都唔執垃圾搞到要出老解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎澳豬對號入座<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8689350f1d2a9aaa512e02434967ffc2f63f927","tid":374417,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T18:14:15.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得，頂道門頂得咁落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe6671e1addc3968c1fcefccd73a2eafa51aed6","tid":374417,"uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T22:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔怪之得，頂道門頂得咁落力<img src=\"/assets/faces